description: These friendly Midwesterners are riding around town in style, and all the while twisting out delicious soft serve ice cream with a bounty of the best and tastiest toppings; fruit, cookies, cereals, and more. They’ve also formed the dream team with Dogwood Coffee, and will be serving up incredibly refreshing Cold Press Coffee Shakes. For sugar, spice, and everything nice, come out and try the delectable desserts from this super cute truck.
name: MN Nice Cream
